Title: Dedicates a portion of the state highway system to Major Andrew D. Byers
Summary: Designates a portion of the state highway system as the "Major Andrew D. Byers Memorial Highway" on state route 324 in the town of Clarence.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the highway law, in relation to designating a portion of the state highway system as the "Major Andrew D. Byers Memorial Highway"
